me.wobblyyyy.pathfinder2.robot.modifiers

Interface Modifiable<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the modified object.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Drive, Odometry
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDrive, AbstractOdometry, EmptyDrive, EmptyOdometry, MeccanumDrive, MeccanumDriveOdometry, SimulatedDrive, SimulatedOdometry, SwerveChassisOdometry, SwerveDrive, ThreeWheelOdometry, TrackableWrapper

    public interface Modifiable<E>
    Something with inputs/outputs that can be modified via a "modifier" function. In the case of this library, the main two applications of this interface are the Drive and the Odometry interfaces. The odometry interface can modify the outputted position. And the drive interface can modify the inputted translations.
    Since:
    0.0.0
    Author:
    Colin Robertson
